   <body>
      <prereq>
         <ul>
            <li>No users are invited to the role.</li>
         </ul>
      </prereq>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>In the module menu, click<uicontrol>Administration</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The<uicontrol>ADMINISTRATION</uicontrol>page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the navigation pane, expand<uicontrol>User Management</uicontrol>, and then click<uicontrol>Security Roles</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The<uicontrol>SECURITY ROLES</uicontrol>list page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select a role and click<uicontrol>Delete</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>A confirmation message is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click<uicontrol>OK</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
